title: Does this picture show a meeting with government officials without masks?
subtitle: A common picture of social media is allegedly shown by Democratic presidential candidate Joe Baiden and Gove Michigan. Gretchen Whitmore in Washington, D.C., no masks.
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: A photograph of Joe Biden ' s meeting with a number of government officials is taken in September 2020, with none of those wearing masks.
